{"id":238639,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-安徽濉溪县访民邵华平起诉公安局未获立/","date":"2012-07-08T22:01:38Z","modified":"2012-07-08T22:01:38Z","title":"维权网 | 安徽濉溪县访民邵华平起诉公安局未获立案（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a>（维权网信息员周维林报道）安徽省淮北市濉溪县访民邵华平反映，她于<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>到濉溪县法院起诉濉溪县公安局，控告濉溪县公安局对其上访进行打压，虚构其到北京使馆区的事实对其拘留十日的行政处罚违法，要求撤销濉溪县公安局濉公（濉）行决字</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[2011]</span><span>第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0125</span><span>号行政处罚决定书。但已经过了月余，法院毫无立案音讯。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span> </p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据邵华平称，她是因所在村庄的塌陷补偿款分配不公而上访，因上访和要求村里公布补偿款总数和分配标准及各户补偿数曾被村长殴打致轻微伤，更多次到北京上访被截访带回后，又被濉溪县公安局行政拘留，其中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>到国家信访局上访，被截回后以所谓的“扰乱国家信访局单位秩序”名义拘留十日，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日到国家信访局上访被截回后，濉溪县公安局警察竟然以“到使馆区上访，扰乱了使馆区的单位秩序”的名义再次拘留十日，在拘留期间饱受恐吓，要求她在补偿协议书上签字。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>为捍卫人身自由，邵华平于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>到濉溪县法院提起行政诉讼，起诉濉溪县公安局的枉法行为，要求撤销拘留的决定，并对她被拘留给予国家赔偿。但</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月份，邵华平前后去法院达四次，每一次法院工作人员皆未给她以是否立案的明确答复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>邵华平告诉本网信息员，她会坚持诉讼，依法维护自己的公民权利，不立案誓不罢休！</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-nsFS_AQj7jQ/T_moLGxuJ5I/AAAAAAAAJFE/Q1LxBFBxn1g/s1600/P1020228.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-nsFS_AQj7jQ/T_moLGxuJ5I/AAAAAAAAJFE/Q1LxBFBxn1g/s320/P1020228.JPG\" width=\"177\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-79iruFH2P5k/T_moNwIoQcI/AAAAAAAAJFM/8LEoNDHdJ1o/s1600/%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-79iruFH2P5k/T_moNwIoQcI/AAAAAAAAJFM/8LEoNDHdJ1o/s320/%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A6.jpg\" width=\"224\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-5229218450326397347?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/e7aa25a8P1020228.JPG-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}